@startuml
title Activity Diagram: Image Editing

start
:User opens an Image;
:Load Image Bitmap;
:Render Image Preview;

repeat
  :User selects Edit Tool (Crop, Rotate, Filter);
  :Apply changes to Bitmap via OpenCV;
  :Update Image Preview;
repeat while (User makes more edits)

if (User clicks Save?) then (Yes)
  :Compress and Encode Bitmap;
  :Save Image to Local Storage;
  :Show "Saved Successfully";
else (User discards)
  :Discard changes;
endif

stop
@enduml
